## Proposed Changes

---
### 1. Dockerfile Creation

I need to create missing Docker configurations to containerize the applications.

#### [NEW] [backend/Dockerfile](file:///e:/DATN-PJIA/PJI-Clinical-System/backend/Dockerfile)
A multi-stage Docker build to compile the Maven project with OpenJDK 17, and then run the JAR with the OpenTelemetry agent included in the [docker-compose.yml](file:///e:/DATN-PJIA/PJI-Clinical-System/docker-compose.yml).

#### [NEW] [frontend/Dockerfile](file:///e:/DATN-PJIA/PJI-Clinical-System/frontend/Dockerfile)
A multi-stage build. First stage utilizes `node:aipine` (npm ci && npm run build). Second stage utilizes `nginx:alpine` to serve static files. 

