## Verification Plan

### Automated CI Verification
- Jenkins will trigger when code is pushed. It will execute backend tests (Maven), frontend tests (npm test), and python tests (pytest). SonarQube will analyze code. If successful, images are built and pushed.

### Manual Verification
- We will manually trigger a test deploy using `docker compose up -d` on the server and check:
  - Frontend accessible at the main URL snippet.
  - Spring boot accessible at `/api/v1/...`
  - RAG service accessible internally through the RabbitMQ and directly queried via `/docs` if exposed.
